Class QuickSorter<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

  • java.lang.Object

    E - object type of the data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sorter<E>

    public class QuickSorter<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends AbstractComparisonSorter<E>
    This class sorts an array of objects by using the Quick Sort algorithm. Implements the Sorter interface.

    Bilal Mohamad
